{"data":[{"date":"09:17 15/08","title":"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 khen ng\u1ee3i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/truyen-thong-chau-a-khen-ngoi-chien-thang-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u1ec3 thao ch\u00e2u \u00c1 theo d\u00f5i s\u00e1t sao c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Pakistan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, trang FOX Sports phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen t\u1eb7ng cho V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Trong b\u00e0i ph\u00e2n t\u00edch m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e2y b\u00fat Gabriel Tan cho r\u1eb1ng, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang d\u1ea7n thay \u0111\u1ed5i tri\u1ebft l\u00fd ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/vn-15342604637281618228882.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, t\u1ea1o th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o so v\u1edbi Pakistan v\u00e0 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 3-0. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng, nh\u1eefng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng. N\u1ebfu gi\u1eef v\u1eefng phong \u0111\u1ed9, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 cho Nepal l\u1eabn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo Gabriel Tan, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u1ecf con Quang H\u1ea3i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u khi ch\u01a1i b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9, s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o d\u00f9 b\u1ecb k\u00e9o xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p d\u01b0\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Sohu c\u1ee7a Trung Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng ASIAD. \"Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m. M\u1ecdi con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd so v\u1edbi Pakistan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 Messi c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 ASIAD. Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSiamSport c\u0169ng so s\u00e1nh gi\u1eefa U23 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Asiad: \"U23 Th\u00e1i Lan ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb Qatar.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c \u1edf \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 l\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. H\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 nghi\u1ec1n n\u00e1t U23 Pakistan 3-0.\"<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng t\u1edd b\u00e1o nh\u01b0 Goal phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Th\u00e1i Lan, STN Sports c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i ph\u00e2n t\u00edch, \u0111\u01b0a tin v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u cho r\u1eb1ng, s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfn xa.<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 d\u01b0 \u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-thay-doi-ke-hoach-tap-luyen-sau-tran-thang-pakistan-168-194505.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Pakistan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-khong-con-co-hoi-da-11m-duoi-thoi-hlv-park-hang-seo-168-194504.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-pakistan-nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra-292-194503.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan: Nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\">C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sergio-aguero-cung-tung-hai-lan-da-hong-11m-trong-mot-tran-dau-nhu-cong-phuong-168-194500.html\">Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2391","checkdouble":"194524"},{"date":"09:25 15/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Indonesia vs U23 Palestine 19h ng\u00e0y 15/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-u23-indonesia-vs-u23-palestine-19h-ngay-158-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Indonesia vs U23 Palestine l\u00fac 19h ng\u00e0y 15/8 (V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asian 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Indonesia vs U23 Palestine 19h ng\u00e0y 158 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Indonesia vs U23 Palestine 19h ng\u00e0y 158 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/u23-indonesia-vs-u23-palestine.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Indonesia vs U23 Palestine</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>U23 Indonesia vs U23 Palestine: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>U23 Indonesia v\u00e0 U23 Palestine \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018. Hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i, U23 Palestine th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 1, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. X\u1ebfp ph\u00eda sau l\u00e0 U23 Indonesia v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a U23 Indonesia l\u00e0 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ch\u1ee5c ngh\u00ecn C\u0110V. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, U23 Indonesia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n U23 Palestine. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf Vinaphone 2018 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh v\u1eeba qua ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 ch\u1ee9 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, U23 Palestine h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u1edbi U23 \u0110\u00e0i Loan. Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn, U23 Palestine su\u00fdt b\u1ecb U23 L\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, m\u1edbi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 2 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, n\u00ean tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o U23 Indonesia \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, th\u00ec c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 99% U23 Indonesia s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2390","checkdouble":"194525"},{"date":"09:40 15/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 15/8: Paul Scholes nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/diem-tin-sang-158-paul-scholes-nhan-xet-buon-ve-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Lopetegui kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Zidane \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u00e0 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m vi\u1ebft n\u00ean m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi huy ho\u00e0ng h\u01a1n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Zidane \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c sau khi \u0111\u01b0a Real Madrid t\u1edbi 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau \u0111\u00f3, Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u01b0\u1edbng t\u00ean l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Zidane. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, sau khi th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn, Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha sa th\u1ea3i ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 51 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Real. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid t\u1ea1i Tallinn v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zidane tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zidane tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/lopetegui-zidane-da-la-qua-khu-voi-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zidane tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn, Lopetegui r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Real \u1edf m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t sau khi Zidane ra \u0111i. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean sau tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cZizou \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u phi th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u, l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch m\u1edbi v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i ph\u00eda sau. Ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf sau khi b\u00e1n Ronaldo \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u euro. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3, Gareth Bale v\u00e0 Karim Benzema \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch m\u00e0 CR7 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cBale l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y th\u00edch th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Bale. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 Benzema. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1ed1t ngay t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i m\u1edbi t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sergio-ramos-len-tieng-ve-cristiano-ronaldo-180-194511.html\">Sergio Ramos: Real Madrid v\u1eabn s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2389","checkdouble":"194526"},{"date":"09:43 15/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs U23 Bahrain 19h00 ng\u00e0y 15/8 (Asiad 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-u23-han-quoc-vs-u23-bahrain-19h00-ngay-158-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs U23 Bahrain l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 15/8 (V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asian 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs U23 Bahrain 19h00 ng\u00e0y 158 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs U23 Bahrain 19h00 ng\u00e0y 158 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/truc-tiep-u19-han-quoc-vs-u23-bahrain-15h00-ngay-5-81533441755.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs U23 Bahrain</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs U23 Bahrain: 4-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad, Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5m HCV b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n v\u1edbi U23 Bahrain. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 kim chi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nOlympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c mang t\u1edbi Indonesia \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh, g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a CLB Tottenham \u2013 Song Heung Min, m\u1ed9t trong 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i trong danh s\u00e1ch.\u00a0 Ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 th\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 n\u00f3i l\u00ean, h\u1ecd ch\u1eb3ng ng\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n v\u1edbi U23 Bahrain, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam \u1edf hai k\u1ef3 Asiad g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 VCK U23 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean, U23 Indoneis v\u00e0 U23 UAE \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u00f2a U23 Uzbekistan (nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1) \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady U23 Bahrain v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2388","checkdouble":"194527"},{"date":"10:29 15/08","title":"Diego Simeone ch\u1ec9 ra y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/diego-simeone-truoc-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mang t\u00ednh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><h2>Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eb1ng x\u00fac c\u1ea3m<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2 2018 gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Atletico Madri mang r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Julen Lopetegui, sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Zinedine Zidane v\u00e0 si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/diego-simeone-truoc-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 ch\u1ec9 ra y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 Thibaut Courtois t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Atletico trong th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Gabi c\u1ee7a Atletico th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Courtois tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 mang \u0111\u1ebfn \"n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: \"\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1ea1c quan<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Atletico Madrid gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Antoine Griezmann, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi b\u1ed5 sung nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Gelson Martins, Thomas Lemar hay Santiago Arias. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Diego Simeone cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u00e0 Barcelona.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span><br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Julen Lopetegui, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi si\u00eau sao s\u1ed1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t l\u00ean ngay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp\" - HLV Simeone \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1: \"R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng h\u1ecd\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Nh\u01b0ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e9m ai h\u1ebft. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebfn th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn theo nh\u01b0 \u00fd mu\u1ed1n\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Diego Simeone s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y khi v\u1eabn v\u01b0\u1edbng \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft t\u1ea1i Europa League g\u1eb7p Arsenal. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Atletico s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Atletico Madrid m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-atletico-madrid-tiet-lo-ly-do-tu-choi-gia-nhap-man-utd-172-194516.html\">Sao Atletico Madrid ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia nh\u1eadp Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-valencia-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-atletico-madrid-180-194372.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Valencia chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao Atletico Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/atletico-madrid-chinh-thuc-co-tien-dao-moi-180-194137.html\">Atletico Madrid CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-bat-ngo-chuyen-huong-sang-godin-172-194125.html\">MU t\u00ednh g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Atletico</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/atletico-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-tien-dao-moi-180-193893.html\">Atletico \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2387","checkdouble":"194528"},{"date":"10:57 15/08","title":"Lopetegui: \"Zidane \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u1edbi Real\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/lopetegui-zidane-da-la-qua-khu-voi-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Lopetegui kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Zidane \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u00e0 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m vi\u1ebft n\u00ean m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi huy ho\u00e0ng h\u01a1n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Zidane \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c sau khi \u0111\u01b0a Real Madrid t\u1edbi 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau \u0111\u00f3, Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u01b0\u1edbng t\u00ean l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Zidane. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, sau khi th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn, Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha sa th\u1ea3i ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 51 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Real. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid t\u1ea1i Tallinn v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zidane tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zidane tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/lopetegui-zidane-da-la-qua-khu-voi-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zidane tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn, Lopetegui r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Real \u1edf m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t sau khi Zidane ra \u0111i. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean sau tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cZizou \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u phi th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u, l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch m\u1edbi v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i ph\u00eda sau. Ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf sau khi b\u00e1n Ronaldo \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u euro. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3, Gareth Bale v\u00e0 Karim Benzema \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch m\u00e0 CR7 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cBale l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y th\u00edch th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Bale. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 Benzema. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1ed1t ngay t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i m\u1edbi t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sergio-ramos-len-tieng-ve-cristiano-ronaldo-180-194511.html\">Sergio Ramos: Real Madrid v\u1eabn s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2386","checkdouble":"194529"},{"date":"10:27 15/08","title":"Klopp c\u00f3 l\u1eddi nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/klopp-co-loi-nhan-gui-hang-tien-ve-chat-choi-cua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf Anfield.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 g\u00e2y n\u00e1o lo\u1ea1n th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Liverpool \u0111\u00f3n v\u1ec1 th\u00eam hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ea3 tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 Naby Keita v\u00e0 Fabinho, n\u00e2ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 khu trung t\u00e2m l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 7, bao g\u1ed3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng Jordan Henderson, Georginio Wijnaldum, James Milner, Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain v\u00e0 Adam Lallana.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Klopp nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/klopp-co-loi-nhan-gui-hang-tien-ve-chat-choi-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Klopp nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hay Emre Can \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus, cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u1edf Anfield v\u1eabn v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng g\u1eaft gao v\u00e0 kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t. Hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai, HLV Jurgen Klopp qua \u0111\u00e2y mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean v\u00e0 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c: \u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i tinh th\u1ea7n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai trong s\u1ed1 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng sung m\u00e3n nh\u1ea5t l\u00fac n\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp ra \u0111\u1ebfn ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, nh\u01b0 Naby r\u1ed3i Gini v\u00e0 Millie \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u1ebfn 13km trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng West Ham. \u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 anh ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e2u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 t\u00f4i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y \u1edf c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u2013 s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft. C\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng Hendo hay Adam n\u1eefa, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. H\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho Liverpool, t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng c\u00e1i \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n sau, Liverpool h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn London l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng Premier League, trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn s\u1ebd \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau g\u1ea7n ba th\u1eadp k\u1ef7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-thang-west-ham-doi-bong-manh-nhat-da-lo-dien-172-194354.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/liverpool-thang-west-ham-doi-bong-manh-nhat-da-lo-dien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-thang-west-ham-doi-bong-manh-nhat-da-lo-dien-172-194354.html\">Liverpool h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t West Ham: \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n?</span><br>\r\nLiverpool ch\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19 b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1ed1n sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham, b\u1eafn ph\u00e1t ph\u00e1o hi\u1ec7u cho c\u1ea3 Premier League r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ngai v\u00e0ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2385","checkdouble":"194530"},{"date":"10:48 15/08","title":"Ramos tr\u1ea5n an Courtois tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n c\u1ea3m x\u00fac","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/ramos-tran-an-courtois-truoc-man-ra-mat-lan-lon-cam-xuc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Real Madrid r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00eam nay, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Atletico Madrid.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Atletico</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m n\u1ed5i lo\u1ea1n \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho Thibaut Courtois khi anh to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00eam nay v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Courtois s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid v\u00e0 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh trong khung g\u1ed7 ngay t\u1eeb ban \u0111\u1ea7u. Run r\u1ee7i thay, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Atletico Madrid.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Atletico Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Atletico Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/ramos-tran-an-courtois-truoc-man-ra-mat-lan-lon-cam-xuc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Atletico Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea n\u0103m 2014, Courtois tr\u1ea3i qua ba m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc \u1edf Vicente Calderon, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vang d\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u01b0 khi th\u00e2u t\u00f3m \u0111\u1ee7 c\u1ea3 La Liga, Copa del Rey, Europa League v\u00e0 Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e0nh ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh Real Madrid \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2013-14.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i 180 \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ec9 sau 4 n\u0103m v\u00e0 gi\u1edd, Courtois s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00ean chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n c\u1ea3m x\u00fac cho c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea v\u00e0 th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Sergio Ramos \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u1ea5n an tinh th\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 hay quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 c\u1ee7a ai \u0111\u00f3. Quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real Madrid v\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y nhanh ch\u00f3ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp, th\u00edch nghi v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n g\u00ec m\u00e0 ph\u00e1n x\u00e9t vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Atletico h\u1ebft c\u1ea3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span><br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Julen Lopetegui, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi si\u00eau sao s\u1ed1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2384","checkdouble":"194531"},{"date":"10:11 15/08","title":"Olympic Nepal \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/olympic-nepal-dat-muc-tieu-co-diem-truoc-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u00e1t n\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng thua Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Pakistan.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/lo-dien-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span><br>\r\n<span>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 VI\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf Asiad 2018 Indonesia, t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam n\u0103m nay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018 g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00f4m qua, Olympic Nepal ch\u1ecdn l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Nepal ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau thua t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u (0-1) b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm (ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 7).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn, HLV Gyotoku Koji kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c khi \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 OlympicVi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai b\u1ea3ng D di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 16/8. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 53 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n chia s\u1ebb: \"T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 ai n\u00ean ch\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 . T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a xem Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng\".\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Nepal \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Nepal \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/kozi_gyotoku.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00d4ng Gyotoku Kozi, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Nepal.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n hai tr\u1eadn n\u1eefa n\u00ean ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Olympic Nepal\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng Kozi c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Nam \u00c1 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e1ng 9 m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Nepal. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t \u1edf ASIAD 18 th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 li\u1ec1u thu\u1ed1c tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i khu v\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nepal, Bal Gopal Maharjan, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a HLV Gyotoku Koji, c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra t\u1ef1 tin. \"Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi khi g\u1eb7p h\u1ecd. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Sau \u0111\u00f3, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi Nepal l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Pakistan, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Nepal. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Asiad\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNepal b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u d\u1ef1 Asiad t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1982. H\u1ecd ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn thua Kuwait 1-3 n\u0103m 1982. T\u1ea1i Asiad g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2014, Nepal c\u0169ng n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D. H\u1ecd thua c\u1ea3 ba tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iraq, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Kuwait, kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o v\u00e0 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 13 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-chau-a-khen-ngoi-chien-thang-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-2018-168-194524.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 khen ng\u1ee3i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-thay-doi-ke-hoach-tap-luyen-sau-tran-thang-pakistan-168-194505.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Pakistan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-khong-con-co-hoi-da-11m-duoi-thoi-hlv-park-hang-seo-168-194504.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-pakistan-nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra-292-194503.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan: Nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\">C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sergio-aguero-cung-tung-hai-lan-da-hong-11m-trong-mot-tran-dau-nhu-cong-phuong-168-194500.html\">Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng H\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2383","checkdouble":"194532"},{"date":"11:14 15/08","title":"Barca l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn MU \u0111\u1ee9ng ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/11/barca-lai-khien-mu-dung-ngoi-khong-yen-voi-phat-bieu-ve-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Josep Maria Bartomeu th\u00ec gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Ariedo Braida c\u0169ng \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cu\u1ed7m ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t Old Trafford v\u1ec1 Camp Nou trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca mua Pogba t\u1eeb MU trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tranh th\u1ee7 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p gi\u1eefa Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Jose Mourinho c\u00f9ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n chia tay Man Utd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, Barcelona l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y. S\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Andres Iniesta c\u00e0ng th\u00f4i th\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thay th\u1ebf anh b\u1eb1ng nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch v\u00e0 G\u0110TT c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca mua Pogba t\u1eeb MU h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch v\u00e0 G\u0110TT c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca mua Pogba t\u1eeb MU h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Barca-len-tieng-vu-chi-130-trieu-bang-mua-Paul-Pogba-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca mua Pogba t\u1eeb MU trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Josep Maria Bartomeu \u00fap m\u1edf quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb b\u1ecf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n n\u00e0y trong kho\u1ea3ng g\u1ea7n ba tu\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 danh t\u00ednh nh\u1eb1m t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u00e1c CLB kh\u00e1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ebf r\u1ed3i m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Ariedo Braida c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ti\u1ebfp l\u1eddi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u00ean th\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea7ng Camp Nou khi tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1i t\u00ean Pogba, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u00f4ng n\u00f3i d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 h\u1eb5ng c\u00f2n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u01a1 h\u1ed3. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed d\u1eabn l\u1eddi ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn: \u201cPogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft li\u1ec7u r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y hay kh\u00f4ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 n\u0103m nay, Barca \u0111\u00e3 chi ra kho\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 140 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 4 t\u00e2n binh, bao g\u1ed3m Arthur Melo, Clement Lenglet, Malcom v\u00e0 Arturo Vidal. N\u1ebfu k\u00edch n\u1ed5 qu\u1ea3 si\u00eau bom t\u1ea5n Pogba, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn con s\u1ed1 chi ti\u00eau s\u1ebd c\u00e1n m\u1ed1c 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Liverpool trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-doi-roi-man-utd-ai-la-ke-dung-sau-giat-day-172-194179.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/paul-pogba-doi-roi-man-utd-ai-la-ke-dung-sau-giat-day.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-doi-roi-man-utd-ai-la-ke-dung-sau-giat-day-172-194179.html\">Paul Pogba \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Man Utd: Ai l\u00e0 k\u1ebb \u0111\u1ee9ng sau gi\u1eadt d\u00e2y?</span><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Paul Pogba \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Man Utd d\u00f9 th\u1eadt hay gi\u1ea3 v\u1eabn t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c l\u00ean qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Li\u1ec7u Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i? Ai l\u00e0 k\u1ebb \u0111\u1ee9ng sau m\u00e0n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2382","checkdouble":"194533"},{"date":"07:07 15/08","title":"Sergio Ramos: \"Real Madrid v\u1eabn s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/sergio-ramos-len-tieng-ve-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lionel Messi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 x\u1ee9 Tango \u0111\u1eb7t ra c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u \"Leo\" \u0111ang t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.</h2><h2>Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Argentina ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina t\u1eeb gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u1ed1n tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu ti\u1ebfp theo. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0m d\u1ea5y l\u00ean nghi v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Messi \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/lionel-messi-khong-len-tuyen-argentina-da-giao-huu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, \u0110T Argentina ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ph\u00e1p. HLV Jorge Sampaoli bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00f2n Messi v\u1eabn gi\u1eef s\u1ef1 im l\u1eb7ng. Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Copa America 2016, &quot;Leo&quot; t\u1eebng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay \u0110T Argentina nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0110T Argentina ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 tr\u00ean AFP: &quot;\u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p, hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ebd l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Messi&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tevez th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Messi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018, Carlos Tevez nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh: &quot;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Messi c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 suy ngh\u0129. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ngay c\u1ea3 trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p anh \u1ea5y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Khi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia thi \u0111\u1ea5u, d\u00f9 t\u1ed1t hay kh\u00f4ng, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch anh \u1ea5y. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eadt t\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Argentina v\u00e0 v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Messi. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u00fac n\u00e0y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, Messi v\u1eeba t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fat an \u1ee7i khi c\u00f9ng Barcelona gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau C\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sevilla. Chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Messi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Barcelona v\u1edbi 33 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Lionel Messi:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/vo-dich-sieu-cup-lionel-messi-lap-ky-luc-moi-trong-mau-ao-barca-180-194357.html\">V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Si\u00eau C\u00fap, Lionel Messi l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/sevilla-vs-barca-sieu-cup-tbn-2018-dem-nay-372-194340.html\">Sevilla 1-2 Barca: Messi v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-108-messi-chinh-thuc-tro-thanh-tan-doi-truong-barca-184-194199.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 10/8: Messi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/cuoc-chien-ronaldo-vs-messi-nong-lan-sang-ca-khoan-du-thuyen-188-193849.html\">Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn Ronaldo vs Messi n\u00f3ng lan sang c\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3n ... du thuy\u1ec1n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/lionel-messi-va-dong-doi-lang-le-ve-hoi-quan-o-barcelona-188-192480.html\">Lionel Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1eb7ng l\u1ebd v\u1ec1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u1edf Barcelona</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/ngoi-sao-messi-tap-luyen-voi-cho-cung-truoc-mua-giai-moi-188-192416.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao Messi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ch\u00f3 c\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2381","checkdouble":"194511"},{"date":"07:07 15/08","title":"\"M.U thua xa Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/mu-thua-xa-man-city-va-liverpool.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Man United, Paul Scholes kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh CLB c\u0169 c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng 2 k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi t\u1edd Daily Mirror, Scholes th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch MU. &quot;So v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Liverpool, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecd v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh&quot;, Scholes cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a &quot;Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&quot; d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho &quot;The Kop&quot; trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. &quot;Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ch\u1eef k\u00fd r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng&quot;.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Scholes n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 MU m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Scholes n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 MU m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/Paul-Scholes-Ryan-Giggs-Gary-Neville.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U r\u1ea5t bi quan v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi th\u00e1n ph\u1ee5c cho Man City c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola. &quot;T\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ea5y MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecd v\u1edbi Man City \u1edf \u0111i\u1ec3m g\u00ec. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n. M\u1ed9t hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi, v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u hi\u1ec3u m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. MU th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng&quot;, Scholes nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u MU nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1eabn c\u1ea3 c\u00e1ch h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd sai, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng MU kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda \u0111ua tranh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y&quot;, Scholes k\u1ebft th\u00fac cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t \u0111\u1ea7y bi quan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8, MU g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang ba t\u00e2n binh l\u00e0 Fred t\u1eeb Shakhtar Donetsk v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 53,1 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Diogo Dalot t\u1eeb Porto v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 19,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Lee Grant t\u1eeb Stoke City v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 1,53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League, MU th\u1eafng Leicester City 2-1 v\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Luke Shaw. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. Gary Neville, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Scholes v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh &quot;th\u1eadt \u0111au l\u00f2ng khi xem MU c\u1ee7a Mourinho thi \u0111\u1ea5u&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League, MU s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Brighton tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 22h ng\u00e0y 19/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo TTVN<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2380","checkdouble":"194512"},{"date":"07:25 15/08","title":"Jurgen Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Liverpool:\"West Ham \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i M.U hay Man City\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/klopp-liverpool-khong-phai-so-mot-nhung-se-danh-bai-so-mot.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018-19 nh\u01b0ng HLV Jurgen Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Liverpool r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u1eb1m trong nh\u00f3m \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</h2><h2>Jurgen Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Liverpool<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, Liverpool c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 The Klopp ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, c\u00e1c m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u00e2n binh Naby Keita c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o LiverpoolWest Ham \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i Man Utd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o LiverpoolWest Ham \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i Man Utd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/jurgen-klopp-canh-bao-liverpool.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jurgen Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Liverpool v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t \u1edf Premier League.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, HLV Jurgen Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Liverpool kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1c quan s\u1edbm b\u1edfi West Ham x\u00e9t cho c\u00f9ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng trung: &quot;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0ng West Ham kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 Man Utd hay Man City&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c qua t\u1eebng tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1ed3i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee3 ai<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Gary Neville nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t r\u1eb1ng Virgil Van Dijk c\u1ee7a Liverpool &quot;gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i v\u1eadt&quot;, v\u00ed c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Jaap Stam. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00f3i \u0111\u00f9a r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Jurgen Klopp c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng &quot;con qu\u00e1i v\u1eadt&quot; nh\u01b0 v\u1eady hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi n\u00e0y tr\u00ean France Football, Jurgen Klopp tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ngay: &quot;Kh\u00f4ng, ch\u1eb3ng bao gi\u1edd. S\u1ee3 h\u00e3i ch\u1eb3ng bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1eb1ng anh ta s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 gi\u1ecdng n\u00f3i quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c, cao \u0111\u1ebfn 1m91 n\u1eefa. Ngo\u00e0i Van Dijk v\u00e0 Joel Matip, ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u1edf Liverpool hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i cao l\u1edbn h\u01a1n t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e2u&quot;.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/jurgen-klopp-phat-bieu-ve-didier-deschamps-184-194483.html\">Klopp: &ldquo;Deschamps khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tr\u1edf n\u00ean nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-ve-co-hoi-vo-dich-nha-cua-liverpool-172-194412.html\">HLV Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch NHA c\u1ee7a Liverpool?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-mat-an-tuong-cua-naby-keita-172-194366.html\">HLV Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Naby Keita?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/naby-keita-ra-mat-an-tuong-cai-gia-cua-su-cho-doi-172-194365.html\">Naby Keita ra m\u1eaft \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng: C\u00e1i gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-giup-liverpool-vui-dap-west-ham-4-ban-khong-go-172-194348.html\">3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Liverpool v\u00f9i d\u1eadp West Ham 4 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-thong-bao-thoi-diem-lovren-binh-phuc-chan-thuong-172-194345.html\">HLV Klopp th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m trung v\u1ec7 Liverpool b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2379","checkdouble":"194513"},{"date":"07:48 15/08","title":"Lionel Messi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/lionel-messi-khong-len-tuyen-argentina-da-giao-huu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lionel Messi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 x\u1ee9 Tango \u0111\u1eb7t ra c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u \"Leo\" \u0111ang t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.</h2><h2>Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Argentina ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina t\u1eeb gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u1ed1n tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu ti\u1ebfp theo. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0m d\u1ea5y l\u00ean nghi v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Messi \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/lionel-messi-khong-len-tuyen-argentina-da-giao-huu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, \u0110T Argentina ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ph\u00e1p. HLV Jorge Sampaoli bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00f2n Messi v\u1eabn gi\u1eef s\u1ef1 im l\u1eb7ng. Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Copa America 2016, &quot;Leo&quot; t\u1eebng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay \u0110T Argentina nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0110T Argentina ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 tr\u00ean AFP: &quot;\u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p, hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ebd l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Messi&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tevez th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Messi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018, Carlos Tevez nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh: &quot;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Messi c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 suy ngh\u0129. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ngay c\u1ea3 trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p anh \u1ea5y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Khi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia thi \u0111\u1ea5u, d\u00f9 t\u1ed1t hay kh\u00f4ng, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch anh \u1ea5y. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eadt t\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Argentina v\u00e0 v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Messi. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u00fac n\u00e0y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, Messi v\u1eeba t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fat an \u1ee7i khi c\u00f9ng Barcelona gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau C\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sevilla. Chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Messi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Barcelona v\u1edbi 33 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Lionel Messi:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/vo-dich-sieu-cup-lionel-messi-lap-ky-luc-moi-trong-mau-ao-barca-180-194357.html\">V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Si\u00eau C\u00fap, Lionel Messi l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/sevilla-vs-barca-sieu-cup-tbn-2018-dem-nay-372-194340.html\">Sevilla 1-2 Barca: Messi v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-108-messi-chinh-thuc-tro-thanh-tan-doi-truong-barca-184-194199.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 10/8: Messi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/cuoc-chien-ronaldo-vs-messi-nong-lan-sang-ca-khoan-du-thuyen-188-193849.html\">Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn Ronaldo vs Messi n\u00f3ng lan sang c\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3n ... du thuy\u1ec1n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/lionel-messi-va-dong-doi-lang-le-ve-hoi-quan-o-barcelona-188-192480.html\">Lionel Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1eb7ng l\u1ebd v\u1ec1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u1edf Barcelona</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/ngoi-sao-messi-tap-luyen-voi-cho-cung-truoc-mua-giai-moi-188-192416.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao Messi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ch\u00f3 c\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2378","checkdouble":"194514"},{"date":"07:53 15/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Kyrgyzstan vs U23 Malaysia 16h00 ng\u00e0y 15/8 (Asiad 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-u23-kyrgyzstan-vs-u23-malaysia-16h00-ngay-158-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Kyrgyzstan vs U23 Malaysia l\u00fac 16h00 ng\u00e0y 15/8 (V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asian 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Kyrgyzstan vs U23 Malaysia 16h ng\u00e0y 158 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Kyrgyzstan vs U23 Malaysia 16h ng\u00e0y 158 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/U23-Kyrgyzstan-vs-U23-Malaysia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Kyrgyzstan vs U23 Malaysia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>U23 Kyrgyzstan vs U23 Malaysia: 1-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng FIFA d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c \u0110TQG, Kyrgyzstan x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 92, h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed 171 c\u1ee7a Malaysia. Nh\u01b0ng x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb, Kygryzstan l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao b\u1eb1ng .<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00e2u r\u1ed3i, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Kyrgyzstan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n n\u00e0o \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, U23 Malaysia t\u1eebng v\u00e0o t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U23 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay. Trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Malaysia d\u1ef1 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018, c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 17 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi U23 Malaysia l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o 8 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Th\u01b0\u1eddng Ch\u00e2u. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean Malaysia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t cho \u00c1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i. C\u00e1c CLB trong n\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c trong vi\u1ec7c &quot;nh\u1ea3 qu\u00e2n&quot; s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 U23 Malaysia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng. U23 Malaysia m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01a1n ch\u1ee5c ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u01a1n n\u1eefa, tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a U23 Malaysia \u0111ang b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n khi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb L\u0110B\u0110 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng, sau v\u1ee5 \u1ea9u \u0111\u1ea3 trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi U23 UAE v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd n\u1eafm r\u1ea5t \u00edt th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U23 Kyrgyzstan n\u00ean U23 Malaysia h\u1eb3n s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd m\u00e0 HLV Ong Kim Swee theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec l\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3, hai \u0111\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd chia \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng cao.&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n+ Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p nhau m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, U23 Malaysia th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 1-0.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2377","checkdouble":"194515"}]}